document_data.name: ''Telbar's Studded Leather Armor''
document_data.mainbody: '''''Telbar's studded leather armor''''' was a set of [[enchanted]] [[studded leather]]s that one belonged to a individual named [[Telbar]].
document_data.Powers: ''Telbar's studded leather armor'' possessed a ''+2'' enchantment.
document_data.History: Telbar famously wore this set of armor but it was not known why or how it left his hands. In [[1368 DR]], the armor belonged to [[Sendai Argrim]], an aggressive [[Amn]]ish nationalist who dwelled to the south of [[Nashkel]].
